<div>
<p>John and Dave kick off this week with two topics no Mac user ever expects to talk about: viruses and defragmentation. Yes, folks, it&rsquo;s true: sometimes you have to confront those things which you just don&rsquo;t want to think about. Then it&rsquo;s off to a more fun topic: integrating cars and technology. Once done there it&rsquo;s time to dive into the mailbag and answer listener&rsquo;s questions on the air! Don&rsquo;t get caught, folks, just listen to your two favorite geeks. It&rsquo;s all part of your balanced (tech) diet.</p>
